OL,3,CTrain drivers from 16 companies will
OL,4,Cstage fresh strikes in May
OL,6,FThe industrial action is to get train
OL,7,Fdrivers, who have not had an increase
OL,8,Fin salary for five years, a pay rise,
OL,9,FAslef says.
OL,11,F"Our pay deals at these companies ran
OL,12,Fout in 2019," the union's leader Mick
OL,13,FWhelan said.
OL,15,F"Train drivers at these Train
OL,16,FOperating Companies have not had an
OL,17,Fincrease in salary for five years.
OL,18,FThat is completely wrong," he added.
